{"tid":1575743,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有個阿叔話係後生仔破壞東鐵","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T06:01:31.000Z","uid":14090,"like":49,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"67387070339d7761397131b1b47695eee6007b79","tid":1575743,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"我笑而不語 即刻加多兩嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話：係啊 屌你老味 聽講呢個係第一步咋 地鐵咁撚離譜 聽講會繼續搞 你夠唔夠膽搭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個廢中嚇撚到仆街 假牙都就跌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我緊係乘勝追擊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我繼續：我係你就唔再屌後生仔 你夠唔夠後生個班做先？講腦你又唔夠人嚟 講武又唔夠 我係你出少句聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲更加驚 嚇到話要沽0066 仲話以後唔再夠膽搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家遇到呢啲唔洗怕否認 佢地得把聲 事實上驚到失禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc888dced27ecf3cec2d0216d48e78ab7d3d24dc","tid":1575743,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ec94255ff7c2167d32bb479ffa74bcc384d94c","tid":1575743,"uid":237300,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家係港鐵管理不善，然後政府係大股東，個矛頭係應該向嗰邊，指返自己友儍㗎？"},{"pid":"60f9f4f5ea539c888e771ff0493d12bbba86f049","tid":1575743,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"牙叔牙伯驚到打比個佢寶貝仔話以後唔敢搭地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問點樣返屋企<img src=\"/ass